QuestData.Title: Insurrection: Missing Persons
QuestData.Description: First Arcanist Thalyssra has requested your aid in searching for her missing people.$b$bShe has a lead from a very unexpected ally.$b$bMeet with her at Shal'Aran in Suramar.
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak with First Arcanist Thalyssra in Shal'Aran.
